<br>
Each person is entitled to their own opinion.  You included.  It would be nice however if you would identify yourself so I wouldn't have to say &quot;heh you!&quot;  We must have a couple of hundred Anonymouses posting here.  Choose any fictitious name if you don't want to say who you are but please choose one and stick with it.  Instead of throwing stones, how about adding something to bring the level of discussion up if you don't like where it is. <br><br>
I would like to clarify a few things to you before someone else decides to take you on.  When you see the copyright symbol, it is because persons on this site have been told to use that symbol so another author or academic doesn't come along and borrow the material without first asking permission and giving due credit.  Personally, I have no intention of writing any books.  However,  I have been grateful to a number of individuals who have written their experiences because those books have helped me to remember portions of a time which were very painful and therefore blocked from memory for years.  To get passed, the past.... one has to remember and integrate those experiences.  So there is a legitimate reason for rehashing and telling the stories.  I hope you can appreciate that it is not wise to only be serious all the time.  I am too serious, but I can appreciate good natured fun to relieve the stress.  It is in fact healtier to dodge, duck and not run in a straight line standing up when you are getting fired on.  Maintaining a sense of humor is important or you go off the deep end quicker, or sucked down into quick sand.  I hope this explanation helps you understand and accept the dynamics of the interaction on this site.  No one is making you buy their book.  You probably can get copies of any of them from interlibrary loan.  So chill out.  If you have any questions or contributions feel free to ask, or let us know who you are and what you want to say.
<p><code>--   (Class Lass) </code><p>


